着老公去陪读靠谱吗？（如果结婚了我是一定会去日本陪他的，总觉得两个人就是要在一起）"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ixvqnz4GX05p9EAMaCDY1MDU1ODQzII6f1IUGMAU4hQNACXIJNDYyNDk0MzEzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"250 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"10_1623355598.0440445","card_id":"Q_464055142","target":{"id":464055142,"title":"美国国家地理正式承认南大洋为地球第五大洋，为什么此前不承认？南大洋有哪些特殊的地方？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/464055142","type":"question","created":1623215768,"answer_count":103,"follower_count":1566,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1135,5112,24158,165368,327660],"comment_count":35,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"过去1个世纪以来，美国国家地理学会将世界海洋分为四大洋，分别为太平洋、大西洋、印度洋与北冰洋。在6月8日世界海洋日当天，美国国家地理学会正式宣布将南极洲周边海域的南大洋（Southern Ocean）认证为世界五大洋之一。 美国国家地理学会专家表示：“南大洋长期以来一直被科学家所承认，但由于国际上从未达成一致，我们从未正式承认过它。不过这个特定区域的海水够独特，有它自己的独立生态，因此我们决定将其独立出来，与原先四大洋地位相等，成为世界五大洋之一。”"},"attached_info":"Cj8Ixvqnz4GX05p9EAMaCDY1NDAyODQ5IJidgYYGMCM4ngxACnIJNDY0MDU1MTQyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"244 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-c2716d42ed19ab069a8a9c0fa10c10f0_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"11_1623355598.0445874","card_id":"Q_464360791","target":{"id":464360791,"title":"如何看待 Epic 平台 6 月 10 日免费送出的游戏《控制》（Control）？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/464360791","type":"question","created":1623337320,"answer_count":56,"follower_count":85,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[216,253,1172,27817,205743],"comment_count":4,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4Ixvqnz4GX05p9EAMaCDY1NDcwODY0IOjSiIYGMAQ4VUALcgk0NjQzNjA3OTF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detai